{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 2084043, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Lightbrand", "body": "Imagine an adventurer's journey in his life so far in Azeroth.\n\nClassic:  Acquire [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=17182]Sulfuras[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=19019]Thunderfury[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=22691]Corrupted Ashbringer[/url] & [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=22589]Atiesh[/url].\n\nTBC:  Acquire [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=29348]The Bladefist[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=28773]Gorehowl[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/itemset=699]Warglaives[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=32483]Skull of Gul'dan[/url] and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=34334]Thori'dal[/url].  Kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=16524]Shade of Aran[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=22589]Atiesh[/url].\n\nWrath:  Acquire [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=46017]Val'anyr[/url] and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=49623]Shadowmourne[/url].  [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=36597]Arthas[/url] dies to retconned [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=13262]Ashbringer[/url] :(\n\nCata: Kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=46753]Al'akir[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=19019]Thunderfury[/url],  Kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=52409]Ragnaros[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=17182]Sulfuras[/url], Acquire [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=71086]Dragonwrath[/url] and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/itemset=1087]Fangs of the Father[/url],  Kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=56173]Deathwing[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/itemset=1087]Fangs[/url] (though he technically died to Dragon Soul).\n\nMist: Acquire [url=http://www.wowhead.com/items=4?filter=qu=5;ty=-6:-5:-7:6:-8:0;minle=600]Legendary Cape[/url], defeat [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=71865]Garrosh[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=28773]Gorehowl[/url], obtain [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=112935/tusks-of-mannoroth]Tusk of Mannaroth[/url], optionally picks up [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=112925]Xal'atoh[/url].\n\nWarlords:  Kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=76407]Ner'zul[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=49623]Shadowmourne[/url].  Kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=78714]Kargath[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=29348]The Bladefist[/url], get [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=113591]another pair[/url].  Kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=77325]Blackhand[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=113979]The Black Hand[/url].  [s]Smash Gul'dan with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=32483]Skull of Gul'dan[/url][/s].  Acquire [url=http://www.wowhead.com/items=4?filter=minle=600;qu=5;ty=-2]Legendary Ring[/url],  [s]and Ultimately kill Grommash with either [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=28773]Gorehowl[/url] again or if you're twisted, his son's [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=112925]Xal'atoh[/url].[/s] Scratch that, instead ram [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=91349/mannoroth]Mannaroth[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=112935/tusks-of-mannoroth]Tusk of Mannaroth[/url].\n\nTo some, our adventurer's actions may sound like poetry to the ears, to some it's borderline creepy.   But as a bonus story, what if I told you on the first visit to [url=http://www.wowhead.com/zone=5094]Blackwing Descent[/url], our favorite adventurer bared an eerie grin throughout the raid...because inside the trusty backpack lied [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=19003]two[/url][url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=18422] heads[/url] that failed to make it to the capital all these years...", "date": "2015-01-07T03:25:13-06:00", "rating": 43, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "When the real villain of Warcraft is you...", "creationdate": "2016-10-21T16:57:20-05:00", "id": 999393, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2084043, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "GalenTheGrey", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2015-07-21T22:36:05-05:00", 8, "Lightbrand"]}
