{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 2279416, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "Radeghost", "body": "Ner'zhul, the Lich King? That's probably for DK artifact questline. If not... [b]Ner'zhul is back![/b] If that's the case, I think Ner'zhul's gonna separate from Bolvar.", "date": "2015-11-23T16:57:08-06:00", "rating": 10, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "id wager that he appears as the final spirit that must be tamed as one of the many spirits that were not freed from frostmourne, forever trapped within the shattered blades fragments....", "creationdate": "2015-11-23T19:23:59-06:00", "id": 913397, "rating": 5, "commentid": 2279416, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "conmanW", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "That would make the most sense since Arthas stabbed Ner'zhul with it in his mind in Rise of the Lich King.", "creationdate": "2015-11-23T20:55:19-06:00", "id": 913439, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2279416, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Reignac", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "what...like king piccolo style where bolvar spits up an egg of all of his evil (Nerzhul)", "creationdate": "2015-11-24T16:28:01-06:00", "id": 913678, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2279416, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "RayCrowl", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Before Arthas donned the Lich King's armor, it was the spirit of the former Orc Shaman Ner'zhul whose soul was attached to the armor and then imprisoned (physically) inside the Frozen Throne. Now Arthas and Ner'zhul's spirit are one and together they are the Lich King. Chris Metzen replied: \"Arthas and Ner'zhul have become a perfect fusion of one being - Arthas' PERSONALITY and body with Ner'zhul's wisdom, experience, power and EVIL.", "creationdate": "2015-11-30T02:25:03-06:00", "id": 914782, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2279416, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "trololo681", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "That was before Arthas stabbed his spirit with Frostmourne. Metzen later said \"Yes. Yeah, Ner'zhul is done. He served us well in that capacity, but really the Lich King idea... really is the ultimate expression, you know, as Arthas or whatever. Ner'zhul's done.\"", "creationdate": "2016-05-25T18:24:51-05:00", "id": 944005, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2279416, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Reignac", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2015-11-23T18:06:29-06:00", 1, "Radeghost"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 2279515, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Gigabear", "body": "Arthas' head was merely a setback!", "date": "2015-11-23T19:26:59-06:00", "rating": 10, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 2279694, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "Goregash", "body": "I hate it when Blizzard ignores Cannon just to try and surprise us.\r\n\r\nNer'zhul is dead, gone, destroyed, banished long before WotLK... The moment Arthas sat down on the throne he destroyed all that's left of Ner'zhul and Arthas himself to become the Lich King with all it's strength and no weaknesses.\r\n\r\nI think it's sad that they have to bring back Ner'zhul while that's obviously a closed chapter. Bolvar is the new Lich King, or the Lich King uses Bolvar's body to move around is more likely.\r\n\r\nBut &*!@ lore, right?", "date": "2015-11-24T03:52:48-06:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Do we REALLY know what Kil'jaeden did to Ner'zhul's original soul? Before turning at least some of it into the LK? And remember, in the original warcraft Ner'zhul could open a lot of portals to infinite worlds/timeways. In wod we met a different-timeway-Ner'zhul.", "creationdate": "2015-11-24T04:35:42-06:00", "id": 913539, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2279694, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Sarthorius", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Well, Ner'zhul was blessed with the power of true visioning.he foresaw most of the things like cataclysm, emerald dream and even Uldum before.There are theories that support Ner'zhul is still \"alive\" and he probably knew that Arthas would die one day.Those theories include that Ner'zhul let Arthas die as he could not control him and picked Bolvar as his new vessel.If you watch Fall of the Lich King video you can hear Bolvar's voice turning evil and orcish at the end of the video.And he has things to settle with Legion so maybe he's playing nice to let Azeroth take care of Legion for himself.", "creationdate": "2015-11-24T09:17:29-06:00", "id": 913595, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2279694, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Kalkreth", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Ner'zhul's spirit is what possesses the armor. If Ner'zhul was gone before his soul being put into the armor, Arthas would not have been corrupted by wearing it in any way.", "creationdate": "2015-11-26T22:09:42-06:00", "id": 914114, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2279694, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Mellro", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Ner'zhul's story never really had proper closure. He was out for revenge against the Legion, then Arthas put on the Helm and they merged into a single being, \"Now, we are one.\"But then in Wrath, Blizzard set aside Ner'zhul and focused solely on Arthas. I think it would be far more interesting if Ner'zhul had always been lurking in the helm, waiting for Arthas to fall. He has been seeking revenge against Kil'jaeden and Gul'dan since before Warcraft II. Legion would be the perfect time for him to resurface and take Bolvar's body as his own.", "creationdate": "2015-11-29T11:29:59-06:00", "id": 914664, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2279694, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Suzaku", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 2279709, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Sarthorius", "body": "So many setbacks for a single guy... Oh wait there's that High (now Blood) Elven King...", "date": "2015-11-24T04:33:26-06:00", "rating": -6, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 2279781, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "Filipse", "body": "Ner'Zhul [b]wasnt ever dead technicaly[/b], he cant die.. [u]his Soul is Bound to the [b]Helm of Dominion[/b][/u] (lich king crown), which makes the wielder Lich King, granting them Dominion over Undead, so likely what we're facing is some aspect of Bolvar, or a memory to some extent.", "date": "2015-11-24T09:01:22-06:00", "rating": -3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "\"What's the truth about the new Lich King?\", Chris Metzen replied: \"Arthas and Ner'zhul have become a perfect fusion of one being - Arthas' PERSONALITY and body with Ner'zhul's wisdom, experience, power and EVIL.\" \"Yes. Yeah, Ner'zhul is done. He served us well in that capacity, but really the Lich King idea... really has the ultimate expression, you know, as ARTHAS or whatever. Ner'zhul's DONE.", "creationdate": "2015-11-30T02:14:13-06:00", "id": 914778, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2279781, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "trololo681", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "\"Ner'zhul is no more. He is consumed. There is only Arthas now... Arthas, whom you shall serve for all eternity.\" (c) Lich Kinghttps://twitter.com/MickyNeilson/status/478313335469785088\ufeff", "creationdate": "2015-11-30T02:14:19-06:00", "id": 914779, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2279781, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "trololo681", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "\"\u201cis ne'zhul completely gone gone?\u201d Far as I'm concerned. :) Does anyone in this universe ever really stay dead?\" https://twitter.com/ChrisMetzen/status/270217646241357824", "creationdate": "2016-10-25T12:40:52-05:00", "id": 1000779, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2279781, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Aquamonkey", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Noooooo...it's false.Ner'zhul is eternal.if you play Wrath of the Lich King,you can find Lich king in Howling Fjord.If you see him and attack him,he says:{\"Shamanism has brought you here... Its scent permeates the air.I was once a shaman.\"} Arthas was not a shaman so Ner'zhul was once a shaman.this mean two spirit in one body.Power of Ner'zhul can make a new Lich King and his power is in helm of domination.", "creationdate": "2016-11-14T12:02:09-06:00", "id": 1008618, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2279781, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 16384, "username": "2000020699147", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2015-11-24T09:10:10-06:00", 1, "Filipse"]}
